# Partial JSON Theme Demo
# Only overrides background and foreground, inherits other colors

Output examples/svgs/themes/partial-json-theme.svg

Set FontSize 16
Set Template macos
Set Theme dracula
Set Theme {"background": "#1a0a2e", "foreground": "#ff79c6", "cursor": "#50fa7b"}

Type "echo 'Partial theme override!'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Type "Only BG, FG, and cursor changed"
Sleep 1s
